http://www.commonlink.com:80/~olsen/COPTIC/ganjaman.html 204.77.198.71 19970106075429 text/html 12450
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: WebSTAR/1.2.5 ID/11095
Message-ID: <aef61b1b.8756@www.commonlink.com>
Date: Monday, 06-Jan-97 02:59:39 GMT
