alink="#FF00FF">

<h1 align="center">Petitions to reschedule marijuana</h1>

<hr>

<p>Red balls <img src="../../images/rd_ball.gif" width="17"
height="16"> are on-site / Green balls <img
src="../../images/gr_ball.gif" width="17" height="16"> are
off-site </p>

<hr>

<h2 align="center"><font color="#800000">On the grounds that
marijuana has medical use in treatment in the United States</font></h2>

<h4><img src="../../images/rd_ball.gif" width="17" height="16"><a
href="/~olsen/MEDICAL/YOUNG/young.html">Alliance for Cannabis
Therapeutics v. Drug Enforcement Administration</a></h4>

<hr>

<h2 align="center"><font color="#800000">On the grounds that
marijuana must be in the same schedule as THC</font></h2>

<h4><img src="../../images/gr_ball.gif" width="17" height="16"><a
href="/~olsen/DEA/dea.html">Carl Olsen v. Drug Enforcement
Administration</a></h4>

<hr>

<h2 align="center"><font color="#800000">On the grounds that
marijuana does not have a high potential for abuse</font></h2>

<h4><img src="../../images/gr_ball.gif" width="17" height="16"><a
href="http://www.natlnorml.org/MSPP.shtml">Jon Gettman v. Drug
Enforcement Administration</a></h4>

<h4><img src="../../images/gr_ball.gif" width="17" height="16"><a
href="http://www.pantless.com/~pdxnorml/brain1.html">Marijuana
and the Human Brain, by Jon Gettman - Part 1</a></h4>

<h4><img src="../../images/gr_ball.gif" width="17" height="16"><a
href="http://www.hightimes.com/~hightimes/ht/mag/957/toleran.html">Marijuana
and the Human Brain, by Jon Gettman - Part 2</a></h4>

<h4><img src="../../images/rd_ball.gif" width="17" height="16"><a
href="jon-01.html">Cannabis Research and International Law, A
Thesis. by Jon Gettman</a></h4>

<h4><img src="../../images/rd_ball.gif" width="17" height="16"><a
href="jon-02.html">The Scientific And Legal Basis for the End of
Marijuana Prohibition.</a></h4>

<h4><img src="../../images/rd_ball.gif" width="17" height="16"><a
href="jon-03.html">Marijuana: What the experts say. by Jon
Gettman</a></h4>

<h4><img src="../../images/rd_ball.gif" width="17" height="16"><a
href="jon-04.html">Substance Abuse: The New Paradigm (1/2). by
Jon Gettman</a></h4>

<hr>

