http://www.commonlink.com:80/~olsen/WAR/padavich.html 204.77.198.71 19970106080604 text/html 10023
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: WebSTAR/1.2.5 ID/11095
Message-ID: <aef61ddc.8810@www.commonlink.com>
Date: Monday, 06-Jan-97 03:11:24 GMT
