HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: WebSTAR/1.2.5 ID/11095
Message-ID: <aef61eba.8821@www.commonlink.com>
Date: Monday, 06-Jan-97 03:15:06 GMT
