<DOCHDR>
http://www.commonlink.com:80/~olsen/MEDICAL/IOWA/grassley.html 204.77.198.71 19970106083902 text/html 15241
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: WebSTAR/1.2.5 ID/11095
Message-ID: <aef6257d.8931@www.commonlink.com>
