<DOCHDR>
http://www.commonlink.com:80/~olsen/MEDICAL/IOWA/olsen-01.html 204.77.198.71 19970106084058 text/html 3364
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
MIME-Version: 1.0
Server: WebSTAR/1.2.5 ID/11095
Message-ID: <aef6260c.8939@www.commonlink.com>
Date: Monday, 06-Jan-97 03:46:20 GMT
Last-Modified: Friday, 08-Nov-96 00:10:47 GMT
Content-type: text/html
