Patients out of Time: a non-profit organization formed to lobby for
patient access to therapeutic use of marijuana has an electronic
bulletin board system.  This bulletin board contains research data,
historical records, legal cases, legislation, and position papers
by organizations relating to the topic of medical cannabis.  It can
be reached by modem at (804) 263-8237.  The internet e-mail address
is: <A HREF="mailto:Mary_Lynn@patient.win.net">Mary_Lynn@patient.win.net</A>
