     [footnote 122]  Id. 

     [footnote 123]  Id. (quoting State v. Olsen, 315 N.W.2d 1, 7 (Iowa 
1982)). 

     [footnote 124]  Id. 

     [footnote 125]  Id. at 1468.  Judge Buckley found it irrelevant that 
