<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" link="#0000FF" vlink="#FF0000"
alink="#FF00FF">

<h1 align="center">NORML's 1996 Weekly Media Releases</h1>

<hr>

<h4><img src="../../images/reddot.gif" width="14" height="14"> <a
href="96-12-19.html">December 19, 1996</a></h4>

<ul>
    <li>Latest High School Senior Survey Data Fuels Anti-Drug
        Rhetoric: NORML Responds To Calls To Escalate Drug War</li>
</ul>

<h4><img src="../../images/reddot.gif" width="14" height="14"> <a
href="96-12-12.html">December 12, 1996</a></h4>

<ul>
    <li>Drug Reform Measure Signed Into Law In Arizona</li>
    <li>(Meanwhile) Drug Czar, Secretary Of Transportation
        Reaffirm Federal Drug Testing Laws</li>
    <li>Dennis Peron, Others To Appear In Court Next Week</li>
</ul>

